title.narrative: Technical Support to Climate Change Institutional Strengthening Programme

description.narrative: This activity (Technical Support to Climate Change Institutional Strengthening Programme) is a component of Tanzania Climate Change Institutional Strengthening Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £605,620. This component benefits Tanzania, and works in the following sector(s): Environmental policy and administrative management. , with the following implementing partners: DAI Europe, Harewelle International Limited. The start date is 15-06-2011 and the end date is 31-12-2015.
